events.name: The first property tech hackathon in Singapore - Hood Disrupt!
events.description: igloohome and district 6 would like to invite you to join Hood Disrupt '17 - Singapore's first ever Property Tech Hackathon! Stand a chance to win cash prizes worth up to SGD6,000 sponsored by JLL, and opportunities to participate in global summits. All participants will also receive SGD100 worth of AWS Cloud Credits for the event. Catch us this 4-6 August 2017, at district6 Co-Working and Offices (Odeon Towers, Singapore). The event is supported by the leading real estate firms in Singapore - JLL, C31 Ventures (CapitaLand's venture fund) and CDL. Other partners include AWS, DreamIt Ventures, Malaysian Proptech Association, Wavemaker Partners and more. To register or find out more information, please visit http://bit.ly/hooddisrupt17fb
events.location: District 6 , Odeon Towers #02-01/08 331 North Bridge Road , Singapore
events.group_name: Hood Disrupt - First Property Tech Hackathon in the Region!
